{"title":"母亲河","authors":["吉狄马加"],"dates":[{"year":2003,"month":3,"day":20}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"母亲河"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吉狄马加（彝族）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"曾记得少年时光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们是多么地快乐"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"漂流在你的怀中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亲吻着水的花朵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是你那美妙的歌声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"陪伴着我的成长"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，母亲河，母亲河"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是你的乳汁养育了我"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当离开你的时候"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们是多么地惆怅"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不知几回在梦中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才感到了你的忧伤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为何你的乳汁已经减少"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是谁改变了你的模样"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，母亲河，母亲河"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是你的命运牵动着我"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我就要回到你的身旁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远不会再离你而去"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让我用双手轻轻地抹掉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你那往日的泪痕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让我用全部的爱情和生命"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"报答你曾给予过我的一切"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，母亲河，母亲河"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是你的希望召唤着我"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":15,"page_end":15}